  "time_ut": 1661935537,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0db1\u0dd9\u0dc5\u0dd4\u0db8\u0dca \u0d9a\u0dd4\u0dc5\u0dd4\u0db1\u0dda \u0db8\u0dd9\u0dc4\u0dd9\u0dba\u0dd4\u0db8\u0dca \u0dc3\u0dd0\u0db4\u0dca\u0dad\u0dd0\u0db8\u0dca\u0db6\u0dbb\u0dca 15 \u0dc0\u0dd0\u0db1\u0dd2\u0daf\u0dcf \u0d87\u0dbb\u0db9\u0dd9\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Operations at the Lotus Tower will begin on September 15",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to the President's Office, the operations of the \"Lotus Tower\", the tallest building in South Asia, are planned to start from September 15.",
        "A spokesperson of the President's Office also said that with the commencement of operations of the Lotus Tower, built at a cost of nearly 113 million US dollars, \"Colombo Lotus Tower Pvt.",
        "The construction of the Lotus Tower started in 2012 and the construction was completed on February 28, 2022 and handed over to the Government of Sri Lanka. For this purpose, the Chinese company has given 88.65 US dollars and the rest has been used by the Government of Sri Lanka. the",
        "The loan installment payments are to be completed by the year 2024. 66.3936 million US dollars in loans have already been paid.",
        "Colombo, Nelum Kuluna Private Company is a company established in March this year under the Treasury, and all its transactions are audited by the Auditor General's Department.",
        "Retired Major General Prasad Samarasinghe, Chief Administrative Officer of Colombo Lotus Tower Private Company, says that it is planned to provide entertainment and new technical experiences like in the rich countries of the world.",
        "Mr. Samarasinghe revealed that so far 80 percent of local investors and 20 percent of foreign investors have invested in the Lotus Tower. Mr. Samarasinghe said that he has discussed with 58 investors and 22 of them are willing to enter into agreements."
      ],
